## Commands Cheatsheet

```bash
# Dir mode — find directories and files
gobuster dir -u "http://TARGET/" -w WORDLIST -t 64 -x php,js,txt

# DNS mode — find subdomains
gobuster dns -d TARGET.thm -w WORDLIST -r DNS_SERVER

# Vhost mode — find virtual hosts
gobuster vhost -u "http://TARGET_IP" --domain TARGET.thm \
-w WORDLIST --append-domain --exclude-length 250-320

# Skip TLS verification
gobuster dir -u "https://TARGET/" -w WORDLIST --no-tls-validation

# Save output to file
gobuster dir -u "http://TARGET/" -w WORDLIST -o results.txt
```

---

## Key Flags Reference

| Flag | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `-u` | Target URL |
| `-w` | Wordlist path |
| `-t` | Threads (default 10) |
| `-x` | File extensions |
| `-o` | Output to file |
| `-r` | Custom DNS resolver |
| `-d` | Target domain (dns mode) |
| `--append-domain` | Append domain to wordlist entries |
| `--exclude-length` | Filter false positives by response size |
| `--no-tls-validation` | Skip SSL certificate check |
| `--delay` | Wait time between requests |

