## Mistakes I Made & Fixed
- Typo: `/usr/share/worldlists/` → correct: `/usr/share/wordlists/`
- Forgot `http://` in URL → got "unsupported scheme" error
- Used `small.txt` wordlist — too small, switched to `common.txt`
- Forgot to add `.thm` domain to `/etc/hosts` → got "no such host" error
- DNS mode needed `-r` flag to point to target's DNS server

